## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Secrets / env
*.env
*.secret
*.pem
*.key

# OS / editors
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Evidence temp
evidence/**/tmp/